			Profile
			
			ShimingGaoreceivedhisB.E.andPh.D.Degreesin2000and2005fromTsinghuaUniversity,Beijing,China,andnowheisworkingasafullprofessorwithCentreforOpticalandElectromagneticResearch(COER),DepartmentofOpticalEngineering,ZhejiangUniversity,Hangzhou,China.
In2011,hewasselectedasthe&ldquo;QiushiYoungScientist&rdquo;ofZhejiangUniversityandwonthesecondprizefortheExcellentScientificAchievementoftheUniversityinZhejiangProvince.In2012,hewasawardedJinGuofanPrizeforexcellentyouthofChinaInstrumentSocietyScholarships.HeisoneofthespeakerteachersofthecourseofFiber-OpticCommunicationsTechnology,oneofthenationalbilingualdemocourses.From2009to2011,hehasvisitedUniversityofCalifornia,Irvine,CA,theUnitedStates,supportedbythe&ldquo;New-StarProgram&rdquo;ofZhejiangUniversityandthe&quot;OverseaResearchProjectforYongBackboneTeachers&rdquo;ofChinaScholarshipCouncil.Hehaspublished&nbsp;100papers,inwhich55papersareSCI-indexed.Hehaswrittentwochaptersintwobooksrespectively,publishedbyIntechPublisher,Croatia,andSciencePublisher,China.Heowns7Chineseinventionpatentsnow.HehaswrittenaninvitedpaperforJournalofOpticalPhysics&amp;Materials,andgiveninvitedtalksintheinternationalconferencesofICOCN&rsquo;10andAPOC&rsquo;05.HeisamemberoftheOECC&rsquo;09ConferenceTechnicalCommitteeforOpticalSignalProcessing.
Hisresearchinterestsarenonlinearopticaleffectsandapplications,especiallythenonlinearapplicationsoftheintegratedsiliconnanowirewaveguides.Astheprincipleinvestigator,hehasfinishedorisundertaking3projectssupportedbyNationalScientificFoundationofChinaand3projectssupportedbyZhejiangProvinceorNationalMinistries.Also,hehasfinished4nationalorprovincialprojectsasabackboneresearcher.
			
				
